-- Czech Plane Returns to Budapest Airport Due to Fire
-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 2013-10-02T10:57:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-02/czech-plane-returns-to-budapest-airport-due-to-fire.html
Ceske Aerolinie crew detects fire
during takeoff from Budapest, CSA says in a statement.
* ATR 72 plane, on regular flight between Budapest and Prague,
returns to airport after shutting down engine, extinguishing
fire: CSA
* No one was hurt during the accident: CSA  To contact the reporter on this story:
